7th Avenue Design Studio Pant - Signature - Universal Fit - Bootcut - Brownstone Heather New York's favorite! Slimming through the hip and thigh, this bootcut pant flaunts a flash of silver with our logo bar on the back; front slash pockets create a sleek appeal.

overview

  1. Zip front with hook-and-eye closure.
  2. Belt loops.
  3. Front slash pockets with coin pocket.
  4. Back welt pockets.
  5. Darts below back waistband.
  6. Available in Petite & Tall.

fit & sizing

  1. Bootcut.
  2. Full length.
  3. Sits just below waist.
  4. Relaxed through hip & thigh.
  5. Inseam: 32 inches.

fabric & care

  1. 65% Polyester, 31% Rayon, 4% Spandex.
  2. Machine wash or Dry clean.
  3. Imported.

7th Avenue Design Studio Pant - Signature - Universal Fit - Slim Ankle - Jacquard A textured jacquard print adds a style jolt to our 7th Avenue Slim Ankle Pant; designed with front slash pockets and a cuffed hem.

overview

  1. Zip front with hook-and-eye closure.
  2. Front slash pockets.
  3. Back besom pockets.
  4. Darts below back waistband.

fit & sizing

  1. Slim leg.
  2. Ankle length.
  3. Sits just below waist.
  4. Relaxed through hip & thigh.
  5. Inseam: 27 inches.

fabric & care

  1. 66% Cotton, 32% Polyester, 2% Spandex.
  2. Machine wash or Dry clean.
  3. Imported.
product_category: Apparel > Pants > All-Pants,Apparel > Pants > Signature,Clearance > Redlines-Pants

title: 46.95 INDUSTRIAL STRIPE C
prod_description:
Black & White Striped Flyaway Cardigan Crisp weather calls for chic layers: this open-front striped cardigan wraps up your look with relaxed and refined style. Features a flyaway design and ribbed trim at the sleeves.

overview

  1. Straight neckline.
  2. Open front flyaway cardigan.
  3. Striped front panels with solid back and sleeves.
  4. Long fitted sleeve.
  5. Ribbed trim on sleeve cuffs.

fit & sizing

  1. Hits at hip.

fabric & care

  1. 53% Cotton, 40% Rayon, 7% Nylon.
  2. Machine wash.
  3. Imported.
